                    "type": "sight",
                    "title": "Tiber Cruise with Aperitif",
                    "description": "{\"sightseeing_id\":169,\"result_index\":11,\"sightseeing_name\":\"Tiber Cruise with Aperitif\",\"sightseeing_code\":\"E-E10-WINEBAR\",\"city_id\":134622,\"tour_summary\":null,\"condition_text\":\"E-voucher. Show the voucher on your mobile device to enjoy the activity.\",\"guidelines\":null,\"additional_information\":\"Please make sure you answer all the mandatory questions during the booking process.\",\"total_duration\":\"1 DAYS\",\"from_date\":\"2024-09-04 00:00:00\",\"tour_desc\":\"See the magnificent city of Rome as you have never seen it before with this one of a king boat tour along the River Tiber. Rome is without a shadow of a doubt one of the most iconic European capitals, and is wouldn’t be surprising if you have already seen all of its most important landmarks on postcards, magazines, television or internet – you might even have already gone to visit them during this very same holiday. But what if you could admire their beauty from even another, more romantic angle? Hop aboard our comfortable boats and see Rome from a truly unparalleled vantage point, the water.<br />\\n<br />\\nTo see the spectacular Roman skyline from an incredible perspective; this is what this special cruise is offering you. As you slowly glide along the calm waters of the Tiber, you will come across most of Rome’s most important sites and icons as well as a splendid variety of some of the city’s most charming bridges, which illuminated as they are at night adopt an even more romantic hue. Set eyes upon Ponte S. Angelo and Vatican City with its renowned Cupola, surrounded by thousands of shimmering lights, and see too the fascinating statue of San Michele on top of S. Angelo Castle.<br />\\n<br />\\nThroughout the voyage, you will be able to enjoy live music and even a wine tasting session with appetisers. In short, this tour has all the ingredients to make the experience truly unforgettable.<br/><br/><strong>Inclusions: </strong>ADMISSIONSINCL,Tickets<br>\",\"plan\":[{\"code\":\"2081691388#TOUR|18:00\",\"languages\":\"\",\"special_text\":\"Ticket 18:00|\",\"tour_details\":null,\"currency_code\":\"INR\",\"offered_price\":3505.19,\"published_price\":3505.19,\"agent_commission\":0,\"cancellation_fee\":\"100.00%\",\"last_cancellation_date\":\"2024-08-31 23:59:59.000000\"}],\"city_name\":\"Rome\",\"country_code\":\"IT\",\"sight_types\":[\"activities\"],\"images\":[{\"image_url\":\"https://media.activitiesbank.com/30923/ENG/B/30923_15.jpg\"}],\"notes\":\"Duration is estimated to be 3 hours based on the evening cruise schedule. Food provided includes wine tasting and appetizers. The activity is suitable for kids, but may be more enjoyable for adults. The relaxation level is high due to the romantic atmosphere and live music.\",\"api_used\":\"deepinfra_llama_3_70b\",\"best_for\":[\"couples\",\"romantic\",\"photography enthusiasts\"],\"category\":[\"cultural\",\"scenic\",\"water activity\",\"romantic\",\"nightlife\"],\"kid_friendly\":true,\"transit_type\":null,\"drop_provided\":false,\"food_provided\":true,\"available_times\":[\"18:00\"],\"pickup_provided\":false,\"best_time_of_day\":\"evening\",\"duration_minutes\":180,\"relaxation_level\":4,\"physical_intensity\":1,\"is_transit_activity\":false,\"unique_experience_rating\":4}",
